Reopened issue "Add SVG as ImagePartType for Office 2016 support" (#204) at OfficeDev/Open-XML-SDK
Events.RelatedBody:
Hi,

Office 2016 now (finally) supports svg as a vector image format (https://support.office.com/en-gb/article/Insert-SVG-images-in-Microsoft-Office-69f29d39-194a-4072-8c35-dbe5e7ea528c)
As far as I can see the OpenXml SDK does not currently have support for this yet (as ImagePartType for example).
Are there any plans of adding it in the future, or any roadblocks that might inhibit implementing it?
